{"tid":875710,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"代言人竟用 iPhone X？Samsung 要求賠償 160 萬美元！","createTime":"2018-10-25T05:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T09:02:55.000Z","uid":60286,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"75c10b5c508ac6854689e3fdecd0805db6a55493","tid":875710,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"現時不少 Android 廠商也會找代言人來推廣其手機，然而不時也會傳出錯用 iPhone 在 Twitter 發帖的事情，事後會如何？沒有人太清楚。<br />\n<br />\n不過今次事件主角俄羅斯節目主持人及女政客 Ksenia Sobchak 就面對很嚴重的後果。The Mirror 報導她在一個電視訪問節目中，竟然拿出 iPhone X，雖然她用紙張儘量擋住鏡頭不讓其他人看到她用的手機。AppleInsider 指 Samsung 可能要求賠償 160 萬美元！<br />\n<br />\n其實這也不是單一事件，過去很多代言人也有用 iPhone 的情況。可以肯定，未來 Android 手機代言人用 iPhone 的事件仍會再次發生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H7YniZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H7YniZ.jpg&h=9800eda9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"437a66d4e72c6f7ffbf793d89e98461f10e73c16","tid":875710,"uid":89514,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f1119157136cd25039c3ab6dc55a27d1f4b1d3b","tid":875710,"uid":1823,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"Note 9真好用<br />\n<br />\n從我的iPhone Xs發送"},{"pid":"43328b85cd8f183c09ee97860df0ec0afd6d312c","tid":875710,"uid":1149,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"S9用家揮手區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從我的iPhone X發送"},{"pid":"d7a7acf7ac294bf6e162c0ed3d9b31aef5753285","tid":875710,"uid":69064,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"傻仔先用APPLE <br />\n根本S9 勁好多 從<br />\n<br />\n從我的iPhone XR發送"},{"pid":"c66b771ab22f568c6261a174da51f6fddc78627e","tid":875710,"uid":478,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T07:50:05.000Z","msg":"又貴又唔好用 都唔明點解個個爭住用apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h